title: U-Boot T1 - T4 (2011) (phillywilly-Sosich) cbr
description:
The Atlantic, March 1945. While the Third Reich faces its last days, a german submarine flees in the direction of Buenos Aires with its mysterious cargo under the watchful eye of an SS officer. A series of inexplicable murders and mutilated corpses turns this secret mission into a veritable nightmare for the forty-six members of the crew.
The Amazon, May 1951. An English cartographic expedition discovers the rotten wreck of a U-boot dating back to the Second World War.
Venice, June 2059. A young Venetian student and his professor are assassinated as they prepare to reveal an unprecedented financial scandal.

enjoy
